# zenduty_tags (Data Source)

```hcl 

data "zenduty_tags" "production_tags" {
    team_id = ""
}

```

`or`


```hcl

output "zenduty_tags" {" { 
  value = data.zenduty_tags.production_tags.tags
}

```



## Argument Reference
* `team_id`(Required) - The UniqueID of the team to query.
